Returns and Refunds - Free UK Returns

In the unlikely event that you are unhappy with your purchase and wish to return it you can, of course, do so. All items we sell are covered by our 28-day money-back guarantee. Just return them to us suitably packaged, in a saleable condition, along with the receipt and we will refund your original payment.

100% Secure

Your peace of mind is our priority.

Our 100% secure website accepts all major credit and debit cards as well as PayPal.

We use industry-standard secure sockets layer (SSL) encryption technology on our site.

This encryption process converts your credit card details into code before securely transferring them.

Alternative Payment Options

If you wish to request payment by bank transfer or to discuss paying in installments please contact us at gb@stanleygibbons.com or commonwealth@stanleygibbons.com

Alternatively please call customer services on +44(0)1425 472 363.

My Collection and GSM subscriptions

When does my subscription begin?

Your subscription will begin with the next available issue.

When does my subscription end?

You will receive a notification four weeks prior to the renewal date of your subscription. This subscription will automatically renew every year until it is cancelled. This can be done from the My Orders page within My Account.

My Collection and GSM subscriptions

When does my online subscription begin?

Please be aware that subscriptions can take up to 72 hours to process, but once activated you will receive a welcome email with further direction. The subscription will begin on the day you are granted access.

When does my online subscription end?

You will receive a notification four weeks prior to the renewal date of your subscription. This subscription will automatically renew every year until it is cancelled. This can be done from the My Orders page within My Account.
